data.description: Immaculate & move in ready Verona model villa in desirable active adult community of Saddlbrooke. This 2 BD/2 BA/1,655 Sq.Ft + Den villa has an open floorplan w/wall removed between kitchen & family room. Kitchen offers plenty of counter & cabinet space, island w/breakfast bar & casual dining space. Spacious master bedroom has sliding glass door to private patio, dual vanities, shower & large walk-in closet.  Home sits on a large triangular lot for added privacy & natural light through the many family room & kitchen windows. Light colored wood plank tile floors throughout the great room, kitchen & den w/newer carpet in bedrooms. Saddlebrooke offers amazing amenities w/ 3 pools, 5 restaurants, 3 gyms, 5 golf courses, 3 clubhouses & all the activities you want. Furnishings avail. on sep bil
